				<outline text="Hitchhiker's Guide to Twitter" created="Sun, 27 Jan 2008 15:03:53 GMT" type="outline">
					<outline text="If there were such a book, it would say, instead of &lt;a href=&quot;http://images.scripting.com/archiveScriptingCom/2008/01/27/dontpanic.jpg&quot;&gt;Don't Panic&lt;/a&gt;:" created="Sun, 27 Jan 2008 15:04:01 GMT"/>
					<outline text="&lt;i&gt;No need for anyone to suffer.&lt;/i&gt;" created="Sun, 27 Jan 2008 15:04:38 GMT"/>
					<outline text="Twitter is not a mail list or a chat room. No one has an investment in anyone else's manners. If what someone says causes you too much angst, just unfollow. It's a single click. " created="Sun, 27 Jan 2008 15:04:43 GMT"/>
					<outline text="More advice for Twitter newbies? Please post a comment. &quot;;-&gt;&quot;" created="Sun, 27 Jan 2008 15:18:58 GMT"/>
