					<outline text="When you drop a picture into the desktop &quot;drop folder&quot; it's automatically uploaded to your Flickr account. Now you can set preferences for tags, the default description, access controls and content categories. " created="Mon, 07 Jan 2008 17:13:33 GMT"/>
